# Agent workflow implementation plans (the /plan skill writes a `plan/` folder
# per feature) are regenerated and don't need to be version-controlled. The
# leading **/ matches any agent_docs tree (./agent_docs and ./sculptor/agent_docs).
**/agent_docs/**/plan/

